
4 questions for CEO.

1)How is our total sales revenue changing over time? Are there any clear seasonal patterns?

2)Which countries bring us the most sales revenue, apart from the UK?

3) What are the top 10 products that customers are buying the most (by sales and quantity)?

4)Do we have many repeat customers, or are most of our sales from one-time buyers?



 4 questions for the CMO.

1)Who are our top 10 customers by sales value, and how much do they contribute to our business?

2)Which countries or customer groups spend the most on average per order?

3)Do customers in different countries prefer different products?

4) How can we identify our most valuable customers and encourage them to keep buying from us?
